data.description: HOLY MOLY - What a home!!  Just.  Simply.  Breathtaking.   The golf course views are stunning and serene with nature all around you.  1100 Foxtail Drive is located approx. 8 miles from the ocean in the highly-desirable Long Bay Golf Club community, a Jack Nicklaus Signature course.  This home was built by a local home builder as his personal residence in 2003 and features 2x6 framing.  The current owner has upgraded most of the home so there are a ton of high-end upgrades throughout the home.  Those upgrades include: 3rd garage bay added in 2018 * New roof in 2012 * New HVAC system in 2013 * New 83-gallon hot water heater in 2015 (lifetime warranty on the tank) * New stainless steel appliances in 2022 (except for the smooth-top cooktop) * New wood laminate flooring in the living room and home office in 2016 * Kitchen island upgraded in 2022, including new kitchen faucet and garbage disposal * Whole house painted on the interior (including all moldings) in 2022 * Home has a transferable termite bond with Anchor Services (retreated in 2022) * Monthly pest control by Anchor Services * Heated/cooled Carolina Room added in 2016 (approx. 16 x 16) * All new shrubs and curbscaping, river rocks added, & landscape accent lighting added in 2014 * New carpet in the primary BR in 2020 * Whole house pre-wired for surround sound.    This gorgeous all-brick single-level home features 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a half bath, as well as a foyer, Carolina Room, and a home office (that can also be made into a 4th BR if you prefer).   Other notable features of the home:  All smooth ceilings throughout the home * Double crown molding throughout * Open floor plan * 12" tile floors in the foyer, kitchen, laundry, all 3 bathrooms, & the hallways * Carpet is only in the 3 BR's * Wood laminate floors in the living room and home office * Ceiling fans in all 3 BR's, living room, office, and Carolina Room * Split bedroom floor plan *  The kitchen is ideally designed with its open concept and features:  Center island with granite counter top * Granite tops throughout the kitchen * Pantry * Undermount porcelain sink * 42" white raised-panel cabinets with brushed-nickel knobs * All new appliances in 2022 (except for the stove top) * Eat-in kitchen area as well as a bar counter.   The primary BR has large picture windows with excellent views of the 3rd fairway of the golf course, as well as an en-suite bathroom.  This bathroom has double sinks, separate shower, jetted tub, a walk-in closet, and a linen closet.  The guest bathroom also has double sinks, as well as a garden tub / shower combo. Your laundry room / mud room is located just off the garage as you enter the home and has a side-by-side washer/dryer (which stay with the home) as well as extra storage closets.  There are a TON of storage areas in this home including 2 attic storage access areas in the 3-car garage.  The Carolina Room has a mini-split unit for heat / AC, EZ Breeze vinyl retractable windows with screens for a "4-season" porch, and great views of the golfers hitting their 2nd shot in the fairway.   At your new home, you also have a rear outside patio for grilling, a bird feeder and bird bath under the trees, and beautiful landscaping (including white river rock, 4 palm trees, curbscaping, and accent lighting). All of this is located on a dead-end street with no through traffic so it's very quiet and peaceful.   1100 Foxtail is NOT your typical standard home - it's a builder-designed custom home with loads of extras and everything is in excellent condition.   This turn-key home is just waiting for you to fall in love with it the same way the current owners did when they first saw it in 2009.  What a simply amazing home!!  No, really, come take a look for yourself and you'll see what I mean.
